Grammar

    0 $accept: program $end

    1 program: stats

    2 stats: stat
    3      | stat NEWLINE stats
    4      | INDENT stats DEDENT

    5 stat: simple_stat
    6     | compound_stat

    7 simple_stat: %empty
    8            | print
    9            | expression_stat
   10            | return
   11            | break
   12            | continue
   13            | global
   14            | nonlocal
   15            | yield
   16            | function_call
   17            | COMMENT_STRING
   18            | assert

   19 compound_stat: if
   20              | class
   21              | while
   22              | for
   23              | with
   24              | try
   25              | match
   26              | function_def
   27              | elif
   28              | else

   29 print: PRINT LPAREN expression RPAREN

   30 expression_stat: expression

   31 expression: expression ADD expression
   32           | expression SUB expression
   33           | expression MUL expression
   34           | expression DIV expression
   35           | expression EQ expression
   36           | expression GE expression
   37           | expression LE expression
   38           | expression GT expression
   39           | expression LT expression
   40           | expression POW expression
   41           | expression MOD expression
   42           | expression AND expression
   43           | expression AT expression
   44           | expression LOGICALOR expression
   45           | expression LOGICALAND expression
   46           | LOGICALNOT expression
   47           | expression IDENTITY expression
   48           | expression MEMBERSHIP expression
   49           | expression EQUALITY expression
   50           | expression RELATIONAL expression
   51           | expression '|' expression
   52           | expression '^' expression
   53           | expression '&' expression
   54           | expression BITWISESHIFT expression
   55           | expression '+' expression
   56           | expression '-' expression
   57           | expression '*' expression
   58           | expression '%' expression
   59           | expression '/' expression
   60           | expression DIVFLOOR expression
   61           | '-' expression
   62           | '+' expression
   63           | '~' expression
   64           | expression EXPONENTIATION expression
   65           | NUMBER
   66           | NUMBER COMMA NUMBER
   67           | STRING
   68           | STRING COMMA expression
   69           | expression COMMA expression
   70           | LPAREN expression RPAREN
   71           | IDENTIFIER ASSIGNMENT expression
   72           | IDENTIFIER
   73           | IDENTIFIER ASSIGNMENT LBRACKET expression RBRACKET
   74           | IDENTIFIER AS IDENTIFIER ASSIGNMENT expression

   75 return: RETURN args_expressions SEMICOLON
   76       | RETURN SEMICOLON

   77 break: BREAK SEMICOLON

   78 continue: CONTINUE SEMICOLON

   79 global: GLOBAL args_identifiers SEMICOLON

   80 nonlocal: NONLOCAL args_identifiers SEMICOLON

   81 yield: YIELD args_expressions SEMICOLON

   82 function_call: IDENTIFIER LPAREN args RPAREN COMMA
   83              | IDENTIFIER LPAREN args RPAREN ASSIGNMENT

   84 if: IF expression COLON stats elif

   85 elif: ELIF expression COLON stats elif
   86     | else

   87 else: ELSE COLON stats

   88 while: WHILE expression COLON stats
   89      | WHILE expression COLON stats else

   90 for: FOR IDENTIFIER IN RANGE expression COLON stats
   91    | FOR IDENTIFIER IN expression COLON stats

   92 assert: ASSERT expression SEMICOLON

   93 block: LBRACE stats RBRACE

   94 class: CLASS IDENTIFIER COLON stats
   95      | CLASS IDENTIFIER LPAREN class_args RPAREN COLON stats SEMICOLON

   96 with: WITH with COLON stats else SEMICOLON
   97     | generator
   98     | with_as
   99     | complex_with_as_stat

  100 complex_with_as_stat: LPAREN args_generator RPAREN AS LPAREN args_identifiers RPAREN

  101 args_generator: generator
  102               | generator COMMA args_generator

  103 with_as: generator AS IDENTIFIER
  104        | generator AS IDENTIFIER COMMA with_as

  105 try: TRY COLON stats except_stat_list else finally_stat

  106 except_stat_list: except_stat
  107                 | except_stat except_stat_list

  108 except_stat: EXCEPT except_expression COLON stats

  109 except_expression: %empty
  110                  | generator
  111                  | LPAREN args_generator RPAREN
  112                  | exception_as

  113 exception_as: IDENTIFIER AS generator

  114 function_identifier_parameter: IDENTIFIER
  115                              | UNDERSCORE
  116                              | IDENTIFIER ':' IDENTIFIER

  117 args_expressions: expression COMMA args_expressions
  118                 | expression

  119 args_identifiers: IDENTIFIER COMMA args_identifiers
  120                 | IDENTIFIER

  121 args: expression COMMA args
  122     | expression
  123     | EXPONENTIATION IDENTIFIER
  124     | '*' IDENTIFIER COMMA args
  125     | IDENTIFIER ASSIGNMENT expression COMMA args

  126 generator: IDENTIFIER
  127          | function_call

  128 class_args: IDENTIFIER
  129           | IDENTIFIER COMMA class_args
  130           | IDENTIFIER LBRACKET args_identifiers RBRACKET
  131           | IDENTIFIER LBRACKET args_identifiers RBRACKET COMMA class_args

  132 finally_stat: %empty
  133             | FINALLY COLON block

  134 match: MATCH expression_stat COLON INDENT pattern_list DEDENT SEMICOLON

  135 pattern_list: pattern else SEMICOLON
  136             | pattern pattern_list SEMICOLON

  137 pattern: CASE expression_stat COLON block SEMICOLON
  138        | CASE IDENTIFIER AS IDENTIFIER COLON block SEMICOLON
  139        | CASE expression_stat IF args_expressions COLON block SEMICOLON

  140 function_def: DEF IDENTIFIER expression COLON stats
  141             | DEF IDENTIFIER LPAREN function_declaratin_args RPAREN ARROW IDENTIFIER COLON stats SEMICOLON

  142 function_declaratin_args: %empty
  143                         | function_identifier_parameter COMMA
  144                         | function_identifier_parameter COMMA function_declaratin_args
  145                         | keyword_args

  146 function_identifier_parameter: IDENTIFIER
  147                              | IDENTIFIER COLON IDENTIFIER

  148 keyword_args: IDENTIFIER ASSIGNMENT expression_stat
  149             | IDENTIFIER ASSIGNMENT expression_stat COMMA keyword_args


